00:16:09.427 --> 00:16:10.720 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
Huh?

00:16:14.224 --> 00:16:16.476 position:50% align:center
[BALZAC]
This is the city you saved.

00:16:16.559 --> 00:16:19.896 position:50% align:center
