burning bright within you.

00:16:42.168 --> 00:16:45.880 position:50% align:center
Like an inferno of
overwhelming passion.

00:16:45.964 --> 00:16:48.925 position:50% align:center
Kinda hard to say.

00:16:49.009 --> 00:16:50.343 position:50% align:center
[BALZAC] Are you bothered
by how much time

00:16:50.427 --> 00:16:53.054 position:50% align:center
