00:17:15.952 --> 00:17:18.455 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI] Yeah, right.
The one "reeling me in" is you.

00:17:18.538 --> 00:17:21.875 position:50% align:center
[BALZAC laughs]

00:17:28.089 --> 00:17:30.759 position:50% align:center
[YUKI] Popular girls
don't wear sports bras.

00:17:30.842 --> 00:17:33.011 position:50% align:center
