00:17:41.269 --> 00:17:43.313 position:50% align:center
[YUKI]
Hosomichi isn't Zaburn.

00:17:43.396 --> 00:17:44.731 position:50% align:center
[RIN]
That's right!

00:17:44.814 --> 00:17:45.982 position:50% align:center
