own heroic potential!

00:17:48.943 --> 00:17:50.945 position:50% align:center
[YUKI]
Uhh...

00:17:51.029 --> 00:17:53.073 position:50% align:center
Sure...

00:17:56.076 --> 00:18:00.622 position:50% align:center
