Taking a detour for fun?

00:18:02.499 --> 00:18:06.378 position:50% align:center
[BALZAC] This used to be
the city of Asakusabashi.

00:18:06.461 --> 00:18:07.837 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
