of his Garann.

00:18:42.288 --> 00:18:43.289 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
Huh?

00:18:43.373 --> 00:18:45.000 position:50% align:center
It's simple enough in theory.

00:18:45.083 --> 00:18:47.043 position:50% align:center
