is a battery girl

00:18:47.127 --> 00:18:48.712 position:50% align:center
with a heart full of passion.

00:18:48.795 --> 00:18:51.548 position:50% align:center
The purer the passion,
the more power unleashed.

00:18:51.631 --> 00:18:55.135 position:50% align:center
