00:19:29.753 --> 00:19:31.171 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI gasps]

00:19:33.089 --> 00:19:36.051 position:50% align:center
[BALZAC] For the record, I
really didn't like you at first.

00:19:36.134 --> 00:19:38.011 position:50% align:center
