00:19:57.697 --> 00:20:00.116 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
Do you want me to punch you?

00:20:00.200 --> 00:20:04.829 position:50% align:center
[BALZAC] Be careful, don't ever
transmutate their passion.

