[BALZAC laughs]

00:20:15.799 --> 00:20:19.678 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI] He never explained
what transmutating even is.

00:20:21.221 --> 00:20:22.347 position:50% align:center
Aw, man.

00:20:22.430 --> 00:20:24.099 position:50% align:center
